==Favoriting avatars==
Users can favorite avatars to save them for later. Favorited avatars will appear in the "favorites" row on the avatar page. By default, favorited avatars are added to a single list that can contain 50 avatars. 5 additional avatar favorite lists can be added to with an active [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat+|VRC+ subscription]] for a total of 6 lists.